You have activated your TSE correctly and the TSE was fully certified by the German Federal Office for Information Security (BSI) on 28.05.2021.

Soon the fully certified version of the TSE will be connected to your orderbird register. Until then, you will still see the status "In Evaluation" on your receipts. As a cash register operator, you are obliged to submit an application for the continued toleration of the use of a TSE with the status "In Evaluierung".
The good news is that you can have your application filled out completely automatically and submit it directly to your tax office within three minutes!
Tip: You can start the application process as often as you like. This gives you the opportunity to download the documents required for the application as a PDF here.
Why do I have to submit an application?
This is the data we send to the tax office for you. Please check and correct possible errors, as you are responsible for the accuracy of the data.
Based on your zip code, you will receive a suggestion for the tax office responsible for you. Please check if this is correct and adjust it if necessary.
Please click on "Download the Letter as PDF". Then send the application including the attachment manually to the above email address of your tax office with your email program.
You are here by cell phone or tablet and nothing happens when you click on "Mail application to your tax office"? Then please open the page on a computer.

You are on this page via computer and nothing happens or you get an "error 400" when you click on "Email Finance Office"? Please click on "Download the Letter". Afterwards you can send the application including the attachment manually to the above mentioned e-mail address of your tax office with your E-Mail-App.
